CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Lineage, Inc. is the world's largest global temperature-controlled warehouse REIT with a large network of strategically located facilities across countries in North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific. Coupling end-to-end supply chain solutions and technology, Lineage partners with some of the world's largest food and beverage producers, retailers, and distributors to help increase distribution efficiency, advance sustainability, minimize supply chain waste, and, most importantly, feed the world.
